<br>
A warrior wielding a SoD and primal in complete NToV gear compared to a wizard using standard spells that EVERY wizard is (technically) capable of getting has good stats but is still doing the same damage.  VI is looking to make classes that are not uber upgraded with uber mobs to become upgraded, much like melee.<br>
<br>
