They could do it with 10 minutes work. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/utorcerarcana.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Torcer Arcana</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br>  Posts: 1164<br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/27/02 5:49 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Absor and Rich Waters on Caster Balance</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  completely disagree. You obviously don't ever work with level 60 uberguild monks and rogues that do 80+khp of damage to a mob.</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
